    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148560/extras/15002cfba59e79d367066b725f279f20.avif?t=1761168739\" width=607 height=90 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148560/extras/8579e254514913bf616e7e0af4d61474.poster.avif?t=1761168739\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148560/extras/8579e254514913bf616e7e0af4d61474.webm?t=1761168739\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148560/extras/8579e254514913bf616e7e0af4d61474.mp4?t=1761168739\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Drift, boost, and spin around corners at BLASTING SPEEDS in Project TurboBlast ,</strong> a Singleplayer + Multiplayer arcade-style racing game blending familiar drift handling of Kart racers and tight responsive controls of classic AG racing games. With a focus on being easy to pick up but difficult to master.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Project TURBOBLAST is my passion project  </strong>. It is a love letter and homage to old school arcade racing games like F-Zero, Hotwheels, CTR and many more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148560/extras/e16a1c58a12ef2db68fb75ff67121ee1.poster.avif?t=1761168739\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148560/extras/e16a1c58a12ef2db68fb75ff67121ee1.webm?t=1761168739\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148560/extras/e16a1c58a12ef2db68fb75ff67121ee1.mp4?t=1761168739\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PLANNED FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Grand prix Mode</strong>  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Multiple GameModes</strong> - Such as, but not limited to; <br>Survival <br>Score Attack<br>Time Attack<br>Knockout Race </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Time Trails, Ghost data + leaderboards</strong> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Online+Lan Multiplayer</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Mod + Workshop Support</strong> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Vehicle Customization</strong> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Driver Customization</strong> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148560/extras/20697457b2a21b65c8d4ead7fc9f327a.avif?t=1761168739\" width=500 height=285 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PLAYTESTING AND SUPPORT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Want to get in on the racing early and offer feedback?</strong> Then you can join the discord! Link found in the &quot;links + info&quot; section along with other platforms</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DONT FORGET TO WISHLIST THE GAME</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Wishlisting puts Project TURBOBLAST on the map for other people</strong> , and notifies you of news and demo releases! So it helps a ton, and is deeply appreciated &lt;3</p>",
